cc:Work.dc:title: Circle Ornate Frame
cc:Work.dc:description: This is one of several frames I recently uploaded, based on the cover sheet on a very old (public domain) piece of sheet music. The songs were old, the frames were awesome, rock on! (This one was highly damaged so it took a long time to synthesize. I love the almost symmetrical feeling of it. I just hope that it isn't an 'O' for 'orifice' or something!)
